high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward to the microwave.
Take the mug from the cabinet above the microwave on the left.
Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge to the left of the lettuce. Close then open the fridge door. Take the mug from the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, stop at the start of the oven.
Put the mug in the cabinet below the sink on the left to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and then right again to stand in front of the microwave.
Open the cabinet above, and to the left side of the microwave and take the mug out.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out again.
Go left and face the lower cabinets below the sink.
Put the mug in the cabinet under the right side of the sink and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room head to the cabinet above the microwave
Open the cabinet and pick up the mug in the cabinet, then close it
Turn right walk straight head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the mug then take it out and close the fridge
Turn left then walk straight towards the sink cabinet
Open the cabinet below the sink and put in the mug and close it
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the cabinet
